description._content: Description: End summit of the Northern Range, showing Cypress trees, growing in the rocks below Mountain Korno, Korno Forest, Elevation 2,600 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: Forest Inspection Hut Diorios, built in 1920 - 21, Diorios Forest, Elevation 750 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
